      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RUBY SLIPPER (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (26.11) in a Grade 5 at Q Lakeside. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Has performed well from this box with a win and two minor placings to her name from six starts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. JAVEN'S SHOT (1) finds it hard to break through. Has finished in the placings two on end now, the latest when third (20.31) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Hard to beat again. THREE GIRLS (5) has missed the frame the last couple but was a Grade 5 winner three back (20.17) at this track over 366m. Can improve sharply here. ROCKET ROXY (4) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
